Package com.sanyavertolet.interview.data.value

Class IterableValue

java.lang.Object
com.sanyavertolet.interview.data.value.Value
com.sanyavertolet.interview.data.value.IterableValue
public final class IterableValue extends Value
A final class representing a value that holds a collection of Value instances. The IterableValue class is used to manage and represent a list of values in an expression.
